        <abstract>
            <p>Sends payment for Francis Darwin’s tutoring. Inquires about possible arrangements for his son Leonard, who is slow and not well, to attend with Francis.</p> 
<p>Asks whether he can have a cutting of GVR’s carrion-smelling <hi rend="italic">Arum</hi> which he needs for an experiment.</p> 
        </abstract>
